{{Quote|Her message sounded urgent. Code Green &mdash; Agent in trouble, pick up immediately.|An Alliance operative|<ref name="TM">''[[Tatooine Manhunt]]''</ref>}}
'''Code Green''' was a term used by [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Alliance Intelligence/Legends|intelligence]]. When used in a transmission, it meant that the [[Agent/Legends|agent]] was in trouble and needed immediate extraction. Alliance [[operative]]s responded to a Code Green from Agent [[Dana (Rebel Alliance)|Dana]], who was undercover aboard the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] ''[[Relentless (Dorja)|Relentless]]''. They arrived too late to save her from [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] execution, but she managed to pass on information to the Alliance that [[Adar Tallon/Legends|Adar Tallon]] was alive and in hiding on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].<ref name="TM" />

